      <li><strong>25+ year service depth.</strong> We service Infratech installations from year-1 new through year-25 vintage with consistent parts availability through Burbank.</li>
      <li><strong>Coastal corrosion expertise.</strong> Marine layer wiring junction service common in Santa Monica, Marina del Rey, Manhattan Beach, Pacific Palisades, parts of Malibu.</li>
      <li><strong>Commercial C/CD specialty.</strong> Solid-state relay diagnostic and replacement, restaurant and hotel patio service.</li>
      <li><strong>Residential luxury market depth.</strong> Beverly Hills, Hidden Hills, Pacific Palisades, Bel Air estate installations.</li>
